{"tid":1677203,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"跑步要申請不反對","createTime":"2019-10-27T03:14:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T03:30:04.000Z","uid":292111,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fa198389932851ebddd72823e8fb4fc128c05513","tid":1677203,"uid":292111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T03:14:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191027/60195604?utm_campaign=hkad_article_share&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=share_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191027%2F60195604%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_article_share%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dshare_link&d=HXPWCXSY8fSkht0R8v8uORzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=7626cb5e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191027%2F60195604%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_article_share%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dshare_link&h=2ace7feb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191027/60195604?utm_campaign=hkad_article_share&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=share_link</a><br />\n<br />\n之後<br />\n不如大家一家人落樓下食個飯都一齊入紙申請不反對通知書<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.hk/tc/residents/government/rights/givenotice/givenotice.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fresidents%2Fgovernment%2Frights%2Fgivenotice%2Fgivenotice.htm&d=HXPWCXSY8fSkht0R8v8uORzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=5ae6926b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.hk/tc/residents/government/rights/givenotice/givenotice.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n大家一齊入紙申請<br />\n<br />\n之後popo就會收到好多申請<br />\n<br />\n做死佢地，咁多份申請書<br />\n<br />\n既然佢地話我地非法集結米一齊入紙<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家諗下當佢地每日收到過千份申請書會點<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1641844/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1641844/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"64ca35bfd93c0c7ba91bc8b9a80e1f118c05137e","tid":1677203,"uid":298802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T03:30:04.000Z","msg":"見到建制派就問佢哋攞咗不反對通知書未 然後報警"}]}